{"tid":1640032,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【國際文宣】支那國會議員資助恐怖份子襲擊平民","createTime":"2019-10-08T22:59:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T01:37:41.000Z","uid":202464,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"66e2dc25f7514763b0fea9e06b0f3b346c70f7ba","tid":1640032,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T22:59:32.000Z","msg":"守護香港大聯盟捐款52萬元<br />\n首先，藍屍的士佬蓄意駕車撞向人群屬「恐怖襲擊」<br />\n<br />\n支那政協/人大等同「國會議員」，佢地而家明目張膽用錢資助terriorist。<br />\n<br />\n我好期待佢地畀人制裁。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&Dagger;*********************<br />\n<br />\n全國政協委員黃英豪與港區全國人大代表吳秋北等人，今日去瑪嘉烈醫院看望鄭姓司機。黃英豪表示，鄭老先生現在受醫院和警察保護，由鄭先生女兒出來接受慰問卡和慰問品。同時，守護香港大聯盟昨日發起內部募捐支援鄭老先生，目前承諾捐款逾52萬元。"},{"pid":"1f901f94e8dc40fcacaf5839bc6569a164d03a3a","tid":1640032,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T23:06:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"633be0be252408c68d0adb25f7831ccfffe74ee5","tid":1640032,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T23:07:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06212cd07f09ec13b0110c34b361cf5843ca4b14","tid":1640032,"uid":163447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T23:09:17.000Z","msg":"twitter time<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db4adb2a701160693e7e008247236cad147bccca","tid":1640032,"uid":39872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T23:11:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8b4e62cd43a904d2e0f5cef06ab231c676a54b58","tid":1640032,"uid":202464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"06212cd07f09ec13b0110c34b361cf5843ca4b14","tid":1640032,"uid":163447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T23:09:17.000Z","msg":"twitter time<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T23:11:50.000Z","msg":"文宣組請跟進"},{"pid":"6